               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾammǝra Mikāʾel “Miracles of Michael”: 12 miracles (fols. 1r-28r)
                     II) Taʾammǝra Giyorgis “Miracles of George”: 3 miracles (fols. 28r-34r)
 III)
                     Taʾammǝra Gabra Manfas Qǝddus “ Miracles of Gabra Manfas Qǝddus”: 3 miracles
                     (fols. 34r-37v)
 IV) Malkǝʾa Mikāʾel “Image of Michael” (fols.
                     37v-45r)
 
 Additio 1.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">

                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
