                  <handDesc>
                     
                     <handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">
                        <seg type="script"/>
                        <seg type="ink">Black, red</seg>The name of the scribe is missing on <locus target="#28r">28r</locus> (space for rubricated name left unfilled).<date/>
                        <list type="abbreviations">
                           <item>
                              <abbr>ለዓ፡ ዓለ፡</abbr> for <expan>ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም </expan> (e.g. <locus target="#7r">7r</locus>, 13v).</item>
                        </list>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; names of the protagonists; elements of
                           the names of the donors; a few lines on the incipit page of Text I,
                           alternating with black lines; titles of the subsections; elements of the
                           punctuation signs and text dividers; elements of Ethiopic numerals; the
                           word salām in Text IV.</seg>
                     </handNote>
                  </handDesc>
                  <decoDesc>

                     <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d1">
                        <locus target="#1r">1r</locus> (incipit page of Text I): uncoloured
                        ornamental band with two lateral extensions reaching the bottom of the page;
                        geometric motifs.</decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#45r">ff. 45r</locus>
                           <desc>-v: Donation note.</desc>
                           
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘአቡነ፡ ወልደ፡ አብርሐ፡ ወብእሲቱ፡ ወለተ፡ ትንሣኤ፡ ወአቡሁ፡
                              አቡነ፡ ገብረ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡…</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/> The note is written in the same hand as the main
                           text. It mentions ʾabuna<note> Walda ʾAbrǝha and his family and states
                              that he donated the book to Tabotä Qǝddus Mikāʾel Śoṭa. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Erasures: 3r, 12r, 15r, 22v, 32v, 39r, 45v.
 -
                           Corrections written over erasures: <locus target="#5v">5v</locus>.
 -
                           Corrections written interlineally: <locus target="#2v">2v</locus>, 6v,
                           10v, 28v.
 - Immediate corrections indicated by dashes above and
                           below the word: <locus target="#41r">41r</locus>.
 - Omitted letters
                           and words written interlineally on many fols., e.g., <locus target="#2v">2v</locus>, 13v, 14v, 15r, 39r, 41v, 42r.
 - Space for rubricated
                           names left unfilled (the name of the scribe is missing): <locus target="#28r">28r</locus>.
 - Lacunae on <locus target="#37v">37v</locus> (erasure or space for rubricated lines left
                           unfilled?).
 - Illegible words have been rewritten with recent
                           ballpoint pen: <locus target="#10v">10v</locus>, 13v, 16r, 37v, 38r,
                           39r.
 - Scribbles and doodles on the inside of the boards and on
                              <locus target="#4v">4v</locus>, 17r, 25r, 31r, 42r, 46r, 46v.</item>
                        <item xml:id="e2">
                           <desc type="findingAid">- Readings are indicated by the names of the months
                              written in the margin or between the text lines of some fols.: ዘኅዳር:
                                 <locus target="#1r">fol. 1r</locus> ዘጥር፡: <locus target="#6r">fol.
                                 6r</locus> ዘመጋቢት፡: <locus target="#9r">fol. 9r</locus> ዘሚያዝያ፡:
                                 <locus target="#10r">fol. 10r</locus> ዘግንቦት፡: <locus target="#13v">fol. 13v</locus> ዘሐምሌ: <locus target="#18v">fol. 18v</locus>
                              ዘነሐሴ፡: <locus target="#20r">fol. 20r</locus> ዘመስከረም፡: <locus target="#21v">fol. 21v</locus> ዘጥቅምት፡: <locus target="#25r">fol.
                                 25r</locus>
                           </desc>
                        </item>
                     </list>
                  </additions>
