               <provenance>According to Additio 1 the Ms. was donated by
                        ʾabuna Walda ʾAbrǝha. He and his relatives
                     are are also mentioned in the supplication formulas, e.g., 4r, 13v, 16r, 18v, 20r, 21v, 25r, 28r, 29v, 31v, 36v.</provenance></history>
